title: Grateful Dead Live at Meadowlands Arena on 1987-04-07
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Minglewood Blues, Friend Of The Devil, Beat It On Down The Line, Stagger Lee, Mama Tried-> Big River, West L.A. Fadeaway, Hell In A Bucket, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Box Of Rain, I Need A Miracle-> Bertha, Ship of Fools, Women Are Smarter-> Drums-> Jam-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Morning Dew-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: The Mighty Quinn
